message.body: Hey babe! What you doing for the 4th of July?
Hey we're probably gonna be working!
:( dang. I was probably going to do the usual, get a bunch of fireworks in blow some stuff up. Probably the farm if you guys have time from work.
Well be at the lake the weekend before the 4th if ya wanna come!
Hhmm... Sounds fun. I love hangin with you guys there.
Well let me know! Well be up Saturday afternoon
